# Tailwind v4 and CVA

- ALWAYS use **Tailwind v4** syntax and avoid legacy syntax. (e.g. `bg-(--color-mint-500)` instead of `bg-[var(--color-mint-500)]`)
- For dynamic/variant classes, use **Class Variance Authority (CVA)** instead of template strings.
- Use **twMerge** when a component exposes a **`class`** / **`className`** prop merged with Tailwind utilities.
